   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td port="p2l">2</td>
    <td>out</td>
    <td port="p2r">2</td>
   </tr>
  </table>
 </td></tr>
 <tr><td>
  <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" cellborder="1"><tr>
   <td balign="left">On the +24 V leg to the Y driver. Larger than X because the Y driver runs two motors in parallel (~2x current). Fast-blow upsized for inrush, as with X.</td>
  </tr></table>
 </td></tr>
</table>
> fillcolor="#FFFFFF" shape=box style=filled]
