   <td balign="left">TRIG <- Mega D12, GND <- Mega GND — direct logic connection, no level-shift/opto on the Arduino side, so the camera shares the logic ground (operator-confirmed working). Firmware sends a ~50 ms HIGH pulse (shorter is ignored). Which Blackfly GPIO line D12 lands on: TBD.</td>
  </tr></table>
 </td></tr>
</table>
